        <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="img/3.svg" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h2>Frequency of residues</h2>
        <br>
        <p>It is possible to evaluate the amino acid count according to activity and determine patterns to analyze trends or preferences according to their activity. Using this information, the sequences' average amino acid frequency was analyzed by activity or category, according to the ten main proposals in our work. The drug delivery vehicle category has a clear tendency to prefer Arginine residues. While signal peptides, propeptide, and transit peptide show patterns of similar amino acid content. However, there are no clear trends for the rest of the activities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
